(secondQuint)The Effect of Healing Touch on Sleep Patterns of Pediatric Burn Patients.

 This study examines the impact of Healing Touch on the quality and quantity of sleep in pediatric burn survivors.

 Polysomnography recordings are obtained in order to assess nocturnal sleep in conjunction with Healing Touch; which is done on 1 of 2 nights during Polysomnography.

 Soft background music is played on both nights.

 Healing Touch is performed by one of 2 Healing Touch Certified Practitioners.

